Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.75,0:01:39.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.69,0:01:43.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like you, I despise Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.86,0:01:46.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.73,0:01:51.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is Naruku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:52.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:57.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku is an awful demon!\NWe must destroy him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:03.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Trying to gain time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.66,0:02:19.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.64,0:02:35.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Inuyasha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:36.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:40.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you destroy the well, Kagome\nwon't be able to return!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:42.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you care if you never\nsee her again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:46.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When she's around, I can't\nfight the way I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:54.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Miroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:56.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:02:59.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:01.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To find Naraku and beat the\nhell out of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:03.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, Shippo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:06.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forget it!\NI hate Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:09.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awright! Please yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:12.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think you were a bit\ntoo rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:16.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Although I understand that you\ndon't want her to get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:18.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you understand, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:20.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're going to look for Naraku...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:23.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but how will you find him?\NYou have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:25.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:26.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.13,0:03:27.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.23,0:03:29.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You sent her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:32.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just because Kagome isn't here now,\ndon't take it out on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:33.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:38.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh well... Let's just calm down\nand think things through!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:39.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We don't have the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:41.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:44.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I, too, want to find him quickly\nand slay him with these hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:48.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fifty years ago, he opened the\NWind Tunnel in my grandfather's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:52.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The curse has carried over\ngeneration after generation to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:54.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:04:00.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not good at thinking.\NYou think of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:03.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These things must be taken\nin order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:08.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, you said you fell\ninto Naraku's trap 50 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:09.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:10.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:13.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you've met Naraku then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:14.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:19.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, you can become\na mortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:21.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you use the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:24.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tomorrow at dawn,\nright here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.15,0:04:26.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will bring the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:32.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.53,0:04:39.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if I met him, he was\ndisguised as Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:41.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know what\nhe looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the strange part.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:44.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't know Naraku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:47.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,yet he disguised himself as\NKikyo and shot an arrow at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:50.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you do something\nthat embittered him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:53.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've never seen his face!\NHow would I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:58.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In any case,\NKikyo was a priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:01.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It could be that Naraku...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:04.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,had something to do with Kikyo\nrather than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:06.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo and Naraku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:13.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:18.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been so long! Is your\nrheumatism better?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not! She had beriberi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:23.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? You're not in uniform.\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:28.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My uniform was dirty...\nwith blood all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:30.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! Now it's hemorrhaging?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:35.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My illness is going from\nbad to worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:43.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha's bleeding hadn't stopped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:46.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was so worried for him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:51.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}When he embraced{\i0} me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:55.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll hold onto this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:58.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What if he did that on purpose\nto get the Sacred Jewel?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:00.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If so, I'll never forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:01.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Higurashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:04.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go stand in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:12.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had never been held like\nthat by a boy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:16.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess he passes for a boy.\NSince he's half-human.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:32.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, with these injuries,\nyou won't be able to fight for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:34.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup! It'll be better\nin a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:36.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Trying to act brave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:37.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:40.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:43.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With that kind of energy, you\nmay recover quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:45.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:51.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,ever since that time my sister\NKikyo was resurrected from mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:58.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My sister said that her Sacred Jewel\nwas stolen by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:02.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you think it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:05.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This man who disguised himself\nas you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:08.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, he could have made his\nescape with the Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:09.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:11.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He tricked you into\nterrorizing the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:14.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and going after the\NSacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:15.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:19.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo sealed you to\nthe tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:22.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did he want to make\nyou despise each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:28.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or was he trying to fill Kikyo's heart\nwith hate and bitterness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:29.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:34.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In Kikyo's possession, the\NSacred Jewel remained pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:37.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But when her heart became\nunclean and hateful...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:42.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Jewel also became unclean\nand filled with evil strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:47.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And at that time, only one person\nwould have hoped for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:52.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you want to go there...\nwhere this man lived?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:59.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My sister had decided so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:01.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But she harbored\na thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:04.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because he was unable to move at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:14.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He called himself Onigumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:20.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He had terrible burn scars over\nhis entire body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:23.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}His face, especially, was\nbadly burned.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:25.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He probably fell from a cliff...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}both his legs were broken.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:30.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still, Onigumo lived.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:31.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was unable to move...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:36.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but he slowly healed and\nwas able to speak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:37.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}However...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:40.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}His true self...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:47.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:48.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:53.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your sister has something\ncalled the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:57.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How do you know\nabout that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:09:00.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All bad men are after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:02.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:05.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I understand that the more\nevil this Jewel absorbs...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:07.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the more evil it becomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:12.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My sister has it under control.\NIt will not go bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:16.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo is always so smug.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:20.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd like to see her\nworried and scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:22.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that would give\nme a rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:25.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:27.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So Onigumo said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:30.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister, I don't like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:32.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:38.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He will probably never be able\nto move from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:41.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shortly thereafter...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:45.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sister sealed you to the tree\nand died.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:50.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Several days later when\NI went there...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:52.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the cave was burned down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:57.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The flames must have\nbeen huge...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:59.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Onigumo was\nunable to escape...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:02.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and perished... leaving no bones...\nnot a sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:03.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or so I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:08.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,C'mon, Old Woman!\NWasn't he human?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:10.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Naraku I seek is\na demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:16.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No matter how weak and evil,\nhe was still human.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:17.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No mistake about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:20.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall we go inside\nthis cave?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:30.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It won't budge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:32.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Unless the well is fixed,\NKagome can't return.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:35.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will I ever see her again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:43.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}When she's around, I can't\nfight the way I want!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:45.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's so willful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:49.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll never speak to\NInuyasha ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:51.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you say Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:05.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Priestess Kaede, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:09.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No grass... not even moss\ngrows on this one spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:15.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is where the paralyzed\NOnigumo rested!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:20.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I feel the spirit\nof a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:22.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The spirit which was\nleft here decades ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:26.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can it be that the one\nwho left the evil here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:27.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so that no grass grows...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:29.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is actually human?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:34.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, it's not human.\NIt's from a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:37.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How can a human\nlike Onigumo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:39.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,possess such evil as\nwould belong to a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:41.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:43.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:45.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:50.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:11:58.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:01.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha... blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:05.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn!\NMy wound has reopened!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:08.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:10.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:13.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am the guardian of Hell,\NRoyakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:18.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Royakan? Are you the demon that\nguards that forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:20.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:23.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, I come to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:29.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:32.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He knows that Inuyasha\nis in no condition to fight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:45.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's useless to fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:48.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's only one thing\nto use here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:12:59.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, come over this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:01.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.38,0:13:11.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a brilliant idea it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.11,0:13:15.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to imbed a Sacred Jewel fragment\nin Royakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:17.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.72,0:13:21.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:24.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My vision's getting blurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:29.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monk, Inuyasha's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:30.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... There's only one way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:34.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I can swallow up Royakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:39.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:13:58.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He escaped...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:04.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I should've made Royakan\na bit stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:07.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:09.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's Royakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:10.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:13.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, Naraku is near.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:14.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:16.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Royakan is probably\nunder control...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:19.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,by Naraku, who has a\NSacred Jewel fragment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:22.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No wonder such a gentle\ndemon like Royakan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,has turned so evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:27.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.69,0:14:30.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're here, come out\nand fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.73,0:14:32.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:37.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monk, Royakan may\ncome again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:39.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We should return to\nthe village.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.57,0:14:42.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:06.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been three days.\NWhy doesn't he come for me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:07.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:10.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo from Group E\nwants to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:14.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Higurashi, how've you\nbeen feeling these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:15.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:19.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really? Then will you go to\nthe movies with me on Saturday?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:21.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On Saturday?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:22.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.28,0:15:24.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It'll be a nice change\nfrom studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:26.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or do you have other plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:28.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Plans... err...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:31.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha might've come\nfor me by then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:33.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:36.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You already stood him up once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- How'd you know?!\N- How'd you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:40.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Excuse us.\N- Give us a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:43.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:46.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you have someone\nelse you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:49.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're always sighing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:52.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not the look of one\nwho's worried about school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:53.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:56.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}After he hugged me\nlike that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:59.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll bet it's\nunrequited love!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:00.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:02.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:04.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who'd like a selfish and\nrough guy like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.22,0:16:06.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Who's she talking about?\N- Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:14.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo! I'll go to the movies with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:16.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really? Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:23.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Besides, why should I be manipulated\nby that stubborn Inuyasha!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:39.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what Inuyasha\nis doing now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:41.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Open! Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:43.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:45.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's useless, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:49.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This hut is plastered with\ncharms to keep demons out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:53.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why must I be\nsealed in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:54.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:57.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please Inuyasha.\NBe still and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:17:00.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your wound isn't\nhealed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:02.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:06.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Eh-heh-heh... Would you like\nme to sleep with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:08.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo... Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:11.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you dare disguise\nyourself like that again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:13.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't get so mad?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:18.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, are you still\nbanging around?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:20.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:23.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Charms are no use if\nyou act like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:25.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lemme outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:29.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Priestess Kaede, please seal\nthe door with the charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:30.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not ready yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:36.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know how eager\nyou are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:38.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but first, the wound must\nheal completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:39.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:42.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't underestimate\nthat Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:46.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that why you made\NKagome go through the well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:49.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha... So that's why\nyou sent her away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:53.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't want to die in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:54.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:57.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I need you to get well\nquickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:59.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop talking like a weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:02.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm ready to fight\nanytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:06.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, just stay still and\nget some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:08.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How many times must\NI repeat myself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:10.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:12.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! His wound will\nreopen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:16.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:19.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:22.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder how Kagome\nis doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:27.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not again! Look, just forget\nabout Kagome already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:31.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as she's alive\nand well somewhere, that's all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:35.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to see anymore\nwomen I know die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:44.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I looked for you, Royakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:48.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:53.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go back! I refuse to\nfight Inuyasha again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:55.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:57.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't want to be sucked\ninto the Wind Tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:18:58.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:04.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will take away the fear\nthat is making you tremble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:07.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S-stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.03,0:19:36.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A sinister wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:42.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Priestess Kaede, take care.\NIt's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:49.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He will not take\na step further!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:58.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!\NWhere are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:02.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened?! He's grown\nmuch bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:06.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are you, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:08.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as our spell\nis active...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.13,0:20:12.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}that hut where Inuyasha lies\nwill be invisible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:17.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But what has happened to this\ndemon? He's different.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:22.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll wager another Sacred Jewel\nfragment has been imbedded in him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.75,0:20:25.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such a pitiful defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:29.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Priestess Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.69,0:20:30.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:31.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:41.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can see you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:43.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:47.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Inuyasha!\N- Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:57.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks for releasing me,\NRoyakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.28,0:21:01.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That old hag and monk\nhad me sealed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:03.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We were protecting him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:05.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such an ingrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:07.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:10.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:23.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha's been thrown!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:27.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha's all talk... His strength\nisn't back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:29.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How'd he get so strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:35.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a giant fragment of\NSacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:38.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.89,0:21:41.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't have 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:42.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:45.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:50.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo! I'll take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:52.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll use my Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:54.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.94,0:21:56.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's poison bugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:03.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:05.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.32,0:23:49.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,50 years ago,\NInuyasha and Kikyo were...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:52.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,tricked into hating and\nkilling each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.52,0:23:54.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was all engineered by\na demon, Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.46,0:23:57.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did he do it?\NWhat was his purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.13,0:23:59.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is his true identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.23,0:24:02.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha's fury and\nlove for Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.00,0:24:06.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,cut through the evil\nand corner Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.07,0:24:12.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next, Inuyasha:\N"Naraku's True Identity Revealed".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.21,0:24:13.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look forward to it!
